  "detailed_description": "Sock Pets is a desktop pet simulation game where you purchase, care for, and interact with a variety of plush pets!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2070160/extras/5446854c83206caad2eb4063b1a81a37.avif?t=1729385827\" width=495 height=495 /></span><br><u><strong>Tell Jokes</strong></u><br>Every pet in Sock Pets has the ability to entertain your young one with a variety of related and age-appropriate jokes to keep your children entertained for ages!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2070160/extras/8c6b632a714127927aa42dc680bb646c.avif?t=1729385827\" width=368 height=395 /></span><br><u><strong>Fun Facts!</strong></u><br>Each sock pet has the ability to tell you family-friendly and age-appropriate fun facts about themselves, learn while you play!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2070160/extras/4399c28e55bed08b06bb21e73ca41335.avif?t=1729385827\" width=398 height=374 /></span>",
